## 7. SENSITIVE DATA IN LOCALSTORAGE

**Title:** Insecure JWT Token Storage in Browser LocalStorage  
**CVSS Score:** 6.5 (Medium)  
**CWE:** CWE-522  
**OWASP:** A02:2021 – Cryptographic Failures  

### Description

Authentication tokens are stored in browser localStorage, which is accessible to any JavaScript code running on the page. This is vulnerable to XSS attacks where malicious JavaScript can extract and transmit tokens to attacker servers.

**Vulnerable Code Location:** `client/js/login.js` (Line 18-19)

```javascript
