## 11. INPUT VALIDATION GAPS

**Title:** Missing or Insufficient Input Validation  
**CVSS Score:** 5.0 (Medium)  
**CWE:** CWE-20  
**OWASP:** A03:2021 – Injection  

### Description

Various endpoints lack proper input validation:
1. Comments have no length limits (max 500 in DB but no app validation)
2. Cowsay accepts unlimited input without character whitelist
